Accessing Small StrongDoppelsemigroup AllSmallStrongDoppelsemigroup is an accessor function for accessing the complete list of non-isomorphic StrongDoppelsemigroup of orders 2 to 5.
<#Include Label = "AllSmallStrongDoppelsemigroup">
The output strongdoppelsemigroup are represented by its operation table for +, *, as given in Section .

Checking Models of Small StrongDoppelsemigroup
"IsASmallStrongDoppelsemigroup" is a function for checking a model against the complete list of non-isomorphic StrongDoppelsemigroup of orders 2 to 5. It returns true if the model is a Small StrongDoppelsemigroup, false otherwise.
